    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in perfect shape, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
