    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six with its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS system fully serviced for optimal volumetric efficiency. The chassis has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Power is delivered through a precise ZF 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, providing exceptional traction. This specimen retains its factory-correct suspension geometry and original cross-drilled rotors, presenting in concours-level condition with zero mechanical or aesthetic compromises. A definitive driver\u2019s car for the serious collector.",
